Doing things that are necessary rather than those that are merely enjoyable is not only helpful, but might also be indispensable for individual success. 
indispensable不可缺少的, 责无旁贷的, 绝对必要的
and it was said that Jet Li was sent to be an apprentice when he was hardly four years old
